price to Hertz, with timing of the deliveries being the key issue, the peop=
le said.</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I remain mostly untro=
ubled by this; as I <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/clic=
