, Helvetica, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -1px; font-size: 20px; border-bott=
om-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; margin: 0px; padding: 16px 0px =
5px;">Banking culture</h2>
</td>
</tr>
</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Would you say that right now is a boom=
 time for investment banks? I am not sure. Statistically it seems like the =
answer is yes. The big banks are <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusi=
ness.com/click/25582014.262653/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2Fy=
dGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMDgtMDMvZ2xvYmFsLWJhbmtzLTE3MC1iaWxsaW9uLWhhdWwtbWFya3MtbW9=
