oster care and this is arguably worse.=E2=80=9D Wieczner reports on the rea=
ction:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In the middle and higher=
 echelons of Goldman, the analysts=E2=80=99 plight received little sympathy=
. Randy Habeeb was working as a trader in the bank=E2=80=99s New York offic=
e when the PowerPoint leaked. =E2=80=9CTo be honest with you, I was actuall=
y really pissed,=E2=80=9D he told me. =E2=80=9CIt=E2=80=99s kind of like an=
